{"tid":123623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國產車連俄、越、巴西都不要，國際市佔率趨零","createTime":"2017-02-17T03:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T14:38:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b244ab94238a5bd717c8fae0e43cbfc3a9fde86a","tid":123623,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:36:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkjam.com/?p=6584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkjam.com%2F%3Fp%3D6584&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f900f597\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkjam.com/?p=6584</a><br />\n曾經，中國產車因為政治和價格的關係，在落後市場有一定的需求，可是近年隨著各地經濟成長，質素及美感均欠奉的國產車已受市場唾棄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n陸媒引述數據顯示，中國十大品牌汽車於2017年整個1月份，在俄羅斯的銷量竟然只有約1460輛，比2016年1月萎縮近4成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/hkjam.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/sketch-1487156308047.png?resize=1024%2C576\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fhkjam.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fsketch-1487156308047.png%3Fresize%3D1024%252C576&h=e5ca1a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n數據顯示，從2012年開始，中國汽車出口量開始出現下降趨勢，2012年中國汽車出口105.61萬輛，此後幾年連續下跌，2015年中國汽車出口量僅有73萬輛，2016年則預計只有64萬輛。<br />\n<br />\n專家表示，這趨勢並無任何扭轉的跡象。中國車出口的主要市場包括俄羅斯、巴西、越南、非洲等地都已離棄國產汽車，中國製造的汽車無論性能、安全性、設計和售後服務等都未達水平，相信要相當長的時間，這局面才有機會轉變。"},{"pid":"d2e9198ee0db83125487d8c22a7abc988b272f11","tid":123623,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f501322d6d099ee4991c6884ce4e749960eb41d8","tid":123623,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:41:28.000Z","msg":"連d垃圾國家都唔用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c04f2402903b649e42f53f609cd903e3595f7cc","tid":123623,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmo